OL,3,CPipes being flushed but hundreds of
OL,4,Chouseholds still told 'do not drink'
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FPipes are being flushed out in a
OL,8,FSurrey village as more than 600
OL,9,Fhouseholds are told not to drink water
OL,10,Ffrom the taps.
OL,12,FThames Water issued what it describes
OL,13,Fas a 'precautionary' advice on
OL,14,FThursday after unsafe levels of
OL,15,Fhydrocarbons were discovered.
OL,17,FIt follows an historical fuel leak at
OL,18,Fa petrol station in Bramley near
OL,19,FGuildford with the petrol entering
OL,20,Finto some of Thames Water's
OL,21,Finfrastructure.
