OL,7,FThe water that is being flushed out
OL,8,Fwill be taken to a nearby sewage works
OL,9,Ffor treatment.
OL,11,FFor the customers affected, bottled
OL,12,Fwater stations have been made
OL,13,Favailable while the repairs take place.
OL,15,FTess Fayers from Thames Water said,
OL,16,F"We are asking 616 Bramley properties
OL,17,Fnot to drink the tap water following
OL,18,Frecent water sampling results.
