OL,7,F"The health and safety of our
OL,8,Fcustomers is our number one priority,
OL,9,Fand we would like to reassure
OL,10,Fresidents that this is a precautionary
OL,11,Fmeasure.
OL,13,F"We are in the process of delivering
OL,14,Fletters and bottled water to the
OL,15,Faffected properties. We are also
OL,16,Fidentifying locations to set-up
OL,17,Fbottled water stations and we will
OL,18,Fshare this information with our
OL,19,Fcustomers as soon as possible.
