OL,7,F"We are already on site in the village
OL,8,Fproactively replacing sections of our
OL,9,Fpipes on Horsham Road to reduce the
OL,10,Frisk to our customers."
OL,12,FThe water company added that work is
OL,13,Ftaking place around the clock to
OL,14,Freplace the water main and to get
OL,15,Fsupplies back up and running.
